cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC

This paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically 3D face reconstruction from depth data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for matching and combining the input depth frame with the database shapes, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also discusses the use of the Kinect camera, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
